<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="16">User Interaction</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">Various user-interaction features are illustrated in the following samples.</Paragraph>


<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>ToolTip Demo</Bold> -This sample demonstrates how to create and customize ToolTips for Essential Chart.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>Zooming and Scrolling Demo</Bold> -Illustrates all the zooming and scrolling operations supported in a chart control</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>Interactive Cursor Demo</Bold>-Used to place the cursor over the specific point in the chartArea or over the segments of the series.</Paragraph>

   
    <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        <Bold>Series Mouse Events Demo</Bold> - This sample shows the various mouse events supported by the chart series.
    </Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>Segment Drag And Drop Demo</Bold>-This feature helps the user to drag the Chart point from one location to another location within the Chart area. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>Multiple Chart Linked Zooming Demo</Bold> -Illustrates the usage of the <Run FontWeight="Bold">Zooming</Run> for all the chart in a window. </Paragraph>
